flow.descriptionCdata:
9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.015c12f8-3477-4f68-8a00-8d496a7f4877.prompt=Enter host\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.0191a2e2-9619-4da9-beac-3a48ab4a32fc.description=
Moves a computer account in a new OU in Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
computerDN - the distinguished name of the computer account we want to move
newOUDN - the Organizational Unit that the computer account will be moved to
username - the windows username to connect to active directory as
password - password for username

Returns\:
The new distinguished name (DN) of the computer account, after it was moved to the new OU.

Responses\:
success - Moving the computer account to a new OU was successful.
failure - Moving computer account to new OU failed.
9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.052609aa-4849-46a4-8937-2475191b336d.prompt=Enter host\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.0827c6fb-6c6f-44d9-b2a6-6655f72fb126.description=
Deletes a computer account from Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
oUDN - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN the computer is in (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)
computerCommonName - the name of the computer (its CN)
username - user to connect to AD as
password - password to connect to AD as

Responses\:
success - computer account was successfully deleted.
failure - failed to delete computer account.

Extra Results\:
computerDN - The Distinguinsed Name of the computer account that was deleted.
9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.0c3c257c-0538-41ca-96a8-660d6b64a32f.prompt=Enter host\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.113b7a76-c47d-4eb9-8c39-653b983dbc89.prompt=Enter host\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.151647be-1e7f-49fb-a8b4-10ac172f8531.prompt=Enter computer Common Name(CN)\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.1640102b-9425-4ebd-9194-96232fc7118b.prompt=Enter password\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.16b1c846-facf-458f-902e-e1dacbec6b59.prompt=Enter username\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.1703f7ba-e282-4d2e-8d9c-b192c7754287.prompt=Enter password\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.1e99cfb5-6394-4922-b8d3-5535ed9784ba.prompt=Enter username\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.26a386da-21b3-4a4e-90b4-c1c4e8a22488.prompt=Enter password\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.274112a2-9727-4836-bc8b-5ca3b9e65486.prompt=Enter new OU's Distinguished Name(DN)\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.27a04534-5874-4368-a841-9a4a5ec47c8b.description=
Checks to see if a computer account is enabled in Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
oUDN - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN the computer is in (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)
computerCommonName - the name of the computer account to check
username - the windows username to connect to active directory as
password - password for username

Responses\:
success - The computer account is enabled.
failure - The computer account is disabled or something went wrong.

Extra Results\:
computerDN - The Distinguinsed Name of the computer account.
9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.2a4e9862-f64d-40eb-81a0-79e453f64c38.prompt=Enter password\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.3e127214-c09c-4608-8301-458aa4093f72.prompt=Enter password\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.4cd129fa-87f0-4a75-ac7f-f97fd5e60b26.prompt=Enter password\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.582680ed-1e65-4f00-a351-69c32ecf072f.prompt=Enter computer Distinguished Name(DN)\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.5a1c8759-2930-4154-a535-b42eaec3b26c.prompt=Enter host\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.634a2035-6c4d-4798-9c34-2b18ba21b6e2.prompt=Enter host\: 9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.645cc71b-b43e-4b42-a0f0-e0de7db0cee5.description=
Gets the name of the OU a computer account is in, in Active Directory.

Inputs\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
rootDN - the distinguished name of the root element whose subtree you want to search in
computerCommonName - the name of the computer account
username - the windows username to connect to active directory as
password - password for username

Returns\:
The name of the OU where the computer account is located.

Responses\:
success - The name of the OU the computer is in was retrieved successfully.
failure - Determining computer's OU failed.

Extra Results\:
oUDN - OU's distinguished name

host - the domain controller to connect to
oUDN - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN the computer is in (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)
computerCommonName - the name of the computer (its CN)

Responses\:

Extra Results\:

Creates a new computer account in Active Directory.

Input Parameters\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
oUDN - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN to add the computer to (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)

Responses\:

Extra Results\:

9fdfb143-f55f-4189-9c90-ec002b852720.description=
Creates a new computer account in Active Directory, performs some operations on it (disables and enables it, searches for its OU, moves it to another OU, resets it) and then deletes it.

Input Parameters\:
host - the domain controller to connect to
OU - the Organizational Unit DN or Common Name DN to add the computer to (i.e. OU\=OUTest1,DC\=battleground,DC\=ad)
computerCommonName - the name of the computer (its CN)
rootDN - the distinguished name of the root element whose subtree you want to search in
newOUDN - the Organizational Unit that the computer account will be moved to
username - user to connect to AD as
password - password to connect to AD as

Responses\:
success - all operations finished successfully
failure - failed to do some operation
